<br>
Our two white horses were awesome! As noted above, disabling models would not allow you to summon a horse at all. However using 3rd person views, or just turning slightly to the left or right allowed me to loot and trade fine. <br>
<br>
Added bennies :<br>
-The Safefall add is worth its weight. Haveing an ability I normally wouldn't have is worth 9k alone. <br>
-Weight ... We went to Rathe last night on a money run, I had over 10,000 coins on me, an agility of 1, and could still move fine. My big problem was the fact that I would accidently dismount and take fall damage from weighing so much! Anyway, 368 weight with only 90 strength is amazing.<br>
<br>
